title: Day 1301
content:
# Day 1301

Day 1 of pat leave. Man it's nice having extra time to enjoy a slow morning, read, work on random projects I've been meaning to do, and enjoy a nice dinner with my family.

Yet, it's 8:30 and my little one is crying and honestly I'm exhausted from a full day. So alas it's time to go to sleep. Until tomorrow anon.

10/13/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
